    "<p>Curator of Flemish painting at the Louvre; professor.": [],
    "Michel's family belonged to the French upper middle class.": [],
    "After graduating from the \u00c9cole centrale des Arts et Manufactures de Paris he worked as an industrial engineer and director of factories at both sides of the Franco-Belgian border.": [
