    "He published a basic overview of sixteenth- and seventeenth-century Flemish painting in 1951.": [],
    "His catalog of Flemish paintings of the fifteenth- and sixteenth century in the Louvre appeared in 1953.": [],
    "As the head of the Service d'\u00c9tudes et de Documentation Michel had a special interest in museum reform.": [],
    "His recommendations were published in 1948, <em>Mus\u00e9e et conservateurs</em>.</p>": []
